  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992240/extras/169295ca2a01c96178a0c2b3e22af40f.avif?t=1761514072\" width=636 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Banebush</strong> is a short and very red creepypasta in the format of a visual novel, inspired by scary tales.  <br>Take on the role of Alexey, who is hiding from pursuit in a place full of ghosts from the past. The village, familiar to him from childhood, comes alive in his memory: terrifying grandmother's tales, carefree childhood days, and... an encounter with a nightmare lurking in the dark forest.🌳 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you dare to step into the fairy tale if it turns out to be real? 💀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992240/extras/811651d90141d71d7a25113f25193637.avif?t=1761514072\" width=636 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992240/extras/e18e13a30aab5460559ed9d977d28600.avif?t=1761514072\" width=636 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ominous black-and-red graphics that create an unparalleled tense and anxious atmosphere. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A nonlinear storyline with several different endings. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious and dark soundtracks in the genres of electronic and dark ambient. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992240/extras/169295ca2a01c96178a0c2b3e22af40f.avif?t=1761514072\" width=636 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Banebush</strong> is a short and very red creepypasta in the format of a visual novel, inspired by scary tales.  <br>Take on the role of Alexey, who is hiding from pursuit in a place full of ghosts from the past. The village, familiar to him from childhood, comes alive in his memory: terrifying grandmother's tales, carefree childhood days, and... an encounter with a nightmare lurking in the dark forest.🌳 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you dare to step into the fairy tale if it turns out to be real? 💀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992240/extras/811651d90141d71d7a25113f25193637.avif?t=1761514072\" width=636 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2992240/extras/e18e13a30aab5460559ed9d977d28600.avif?t=1761514072\" width=636 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ominous black-and-red graphics that create an unparalleled tense and anxious atmosphere. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A nonlinear storyline with several different endings. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious and dark soundtracks in the genres of electronic and dark ambient. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
